description._content: Series: NRS16410 - Albums of Travel and Advertising Brochures Title: Canberra City of Sunshine all year round Dated: 01/01/1938 Item: [4_3A] Rights: No known copyright restrictions www.records.nsw.gov.au/about-us/rights-and-permissions To celebrate the centenary of Canberra we have a new Digital Gallery highlighting a record series that sheds light on the efforts of a number of towns, villages and other areas that proudly presented their submissions to become the capital of the new Commonwealth. View the Canberra Digital Gallery More information about this record is in our catalogue, 16410. We'd love to hear from you if you use our photos/documents. Many other photos in our collection are available to view and browse on our website using Photo Investigator.
